{panel:bgColor=#deebff}
*User Story*

With the RTE Systems rotation including members across CA and DE beginning in Q4 2025, we need to remove the team from the [EXCLUDED_TERMS|https://github.com/hellofresh/opsgenie-automation/blob/master/plex/plex.py#L77] in OpsGenie so the DE-based members of the rotation got automatically compensated via Payroll.

This was fine previous to Q4 2025, as all members of the rotation were Canada-based, and they got compensated manually via a process followed by the North American payroll team. We now need this automation running to properly compensate the DE-based members of the rotation.

See members of rotation here: [https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1fdCqOKFMIJSQfXVfQmQaG1MiLU5BRDymsgmsNOlvKWc/edit?gid=1109514217#gid=1109514217|https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1fdCqOKFMIJSQfXVfQmQaG1MiLU5BRDymsgmsNOlvKWc/edit?gid=1109514217#gid=1109514217|smart-link] 
{panel}

