{panel:bgColor=#deebff}
*User Story*

As a HelloFresh or migrated Green Chef customer, I want to be able to switch between "Classic" and "Premium" plans within my account settings so that I can easily upgrade or downgrade my subscription tier.
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#e3fcef}
*Acceptance Criteria*

When the user:

* selects "Premium Plan" -> the user's subscription SKU is updated to the Premium Tier product family (e.g., {{NL-PB-2-2-0}}) via a {{PATCH}} request.
* selects "Classic Plan" -> the user is reverted to the standard product family (e.g., {{NL-CBT19-2-2-0}}).
{panel}

{panel:bgColor=#eae6ff}
*Dev Notes:*

# *API Call:* Use {{PATCH /api/subscriptions/{id}}}. Payload example: {{{"subscription": {"product": {"sku": "NL-PB-2-2-0"}}}}}
# *Context:* This component is shared across Web and Native Apps (via Webview). Testing must include changing the browser user agent to iOS/Android to verify the view within the app container
*Reference:* See specific PR linked in PRD for similar logic: [https://github.com/hellofresh/web/pull/58257|https://github.com/hellofresh/web/pull/58257|smart-link]  
{panel}

