h2. *Description:*

Since the voucher banner in the Funnel flow is a critical path, we need to add tracing to track when this component is rendered to catch issues of banner not being displayed. This will provide visibility into component lifecycle and help identify rendering issues.

This aims to cover the following critical path:

{panel}

|Flow|Expected behavior|Wrong behavior|
|Checkout|Customer with voucher attached sees top discount banner in funnel indicating their discount amount (relevant for box discounts & free add on discounts)|Customer with voucher attached does not see top discount banner|

{panel:bgColor=#e3fcef}
h2. Acceptance Criteria

Trace is added to component rendering that allows tracking when the banner is displayed (or not displayed) to customers, making it easier to diagnose banner visibility issues.
{panel}

